Tallon Zek<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E6E6FA><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub18.ezboard.com/udalrekscalebane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dalrek Scalebane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>MithMarr Defender<BR><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/shellene/star.gif height=10 width=11 border=0></span><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#4B0082>(11/3/01 8:44:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: LoTD </span><hr size=1> First of all, CW didnt start this thread, so dont say we came here crying. CW maybe very clear in guildchat that we would not have a flame war after what happened and some of our members with hot tempers left sol b to avoid that. Rezthe congratulated the LoTD cleric.<br>
