<br>
The facts remain that Rezthe lost her pearl and LoTD looted the heart. I would love to think that if we had camped RF again, then LoTD would have rushed to our aid and triggered for us when it popped again. I just have a hard time believing that you would do that.<br>
<br>
- Dalrek Scalebane<br>
